PhylogeneticData::usage="PhylogeneticData[\"\!\(\*
StyleBox[\"name\",\nFontSlant->\"Italic\"]\)\"] returns the phylogenetic example data corresponding to \"\!\(\*
StyleBox[\"name\",\nFontSlant->\"Italic\"]\)\". PhylogeneticData[\"Names\"] returns available names. PhylogeneticData[All] returns all phylogenetic examples.";


Begin["`Private`"];


